       </label>
       <br class="clear"/>
       <label class="check">
        <input class="check" id="gardens" name="options[]" type="checkbox" value="Making a trip to the Japanese Gardens in Urbana"/>
        Make a trip to the Japanese Gardens in Urbana
       </label>
       <br class="clear"/>
       <label class="check">
        <input class="check" id="dinner" name="options[]" type="checkbox" value="Going out to dinner"/>
        Go out to dinner
       </label>
       <br class="clear"/>
       <label class="check">
        <input class="check" id="list" name="options[]" type="checkbox" value="Making a bucket list and trying to complete as many things as possible before the day ends"/>
        Make a bucket list and try to complete as many things as possible before the day ends
       </label>
       <br class="clear"/>
       <label class="check">
        <input class="check" id="read" name="options[]" type="checkbox" value="Reading a book"/>
        Read a book
       </label>
       <br class="clear"/>
       <label class="check">
        <input class="check" id="play" name="options[]" type="checkbox" value="Playing a game of catch with a friend"/>
        Play a game of catch with a friend
       </label>
       <br class="clear"/>
       <label class="check">
        <input class="check" id="bake" name="options[]" type="checkbox" value="Baking cookies"/>
