    <div class="section">
     <h2 id="cycle">
      Featured Graphics
     </h2>
     <div class="slider">
      <ul class="slider__wrapper">
       <li class="slider__item">
        <a href="#cycle" title="Link to rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
         <img alt="Re-Think The Drink graphic." src="img/rttd-2018/rttd-saysomething.jpg"/>
        </a>
        <div class="offscreen">
         <h3>
          Re-Think The Drink
         </h3>
         <p>
          Say something if someone has had too much to drink.
         </p>
         <p>
          Help make a better Illini community for all and
          <a href="http://rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
           Re-Think The Drink
          </a>
          .
         </p>
        </div>
       </li>
       <li class="slider__item">
        <a href="#cycle" title="Link to rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
         <img alt="Re-Think The Drink graphic." src="img/rttd-2018/rttd-water.jpg"/>
        </a>
        <div class="offscreen">
         <h3>
          Re-Think The Drink
         </h3>
         <p>
          Drink water and eat before and while you drink alcohol.
         </p>
         <p>
          This helps your body slow down how quickly the alcohol is absorbed, stay hydrated, and avoid negative effects.
         </p>
         <p>
          Respect your body and
          <a href="http://rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
           Re-Think The Drink
          </a>
          .
         </p>
        </div>
       </li>
       <li class="slider__item">
        <a href="#cycle" title="Link to rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
         <img alt="Re-Think The Drink graphic." src="img/rttd-2018/rttd-poisoning.jpg"/>
        </a>
        <div class="offscreen">
         <h3>
          Re-Think The Drink
         </h3>
         <p>
          Know the signs of alcohol poisoning.
         </p>
         <p>
          Symptoms include vomitting, slow and irregular breathing, low body temperature, passing out, and pale skin.
          <strong>
           Call 911 if you notice these signs.
          </strong>
         </p>
         <p>
          Source:
          <a href="http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/alcohol-poisoning/basics/symptoms/con-20029020">
           www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/alcohol-poisoning/basics/symptoms/con-20029020
          </a>
         </p>
         <p>
          Help make a better Illini community for all and
          <a href="http://rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
           Re-Think The Drink
          </a>
          .
         </p>
        </div>
       </li>
       <li class="slider__item">
        <a href="#cycle" title="Link to rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
         <img alt="Re-Think The Drink graphic." src="img/rttd-2018/rttd-limits.jpg"/>
        </a>
        <div class="offscreen">
         <h3>
          Re-Think The Drink
         </h3>
         <p>
          Set your own limits, count your drinks, alternate alcohol and non-alcoholic drinks, and pace yourself.
         </p>
         <p>
          Respect other people and their limits and
          <a href="http://rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
           Re-Think The Drink
          </a>
          .
         </p>
        </div>
       </li>
       <li class="slider__item">
        <a href="#cycle" title="Link to rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
         <img alt="Re-Think The Drink graphic." src="img/rttd-2018/rttd-driver.jpg"/>
        </a>
        <div class="offscreen">
         <h3>
          Re-Think The Drink
         </h3>
         <p>
          Driving while intoxicated can cost you. Have a plan to get home.
         </p>
         <p>
          Help make a better Illini community for all and
          <a href="http://rethinkthedrink.illinois.edu">
           Re-Think The Drink
          </a>
          .
         </p>
        </div>
       </li>
      </ul>
     </div>
